item.title: Researach paper
item.dc:creator: @Elrick Elrick
item.description:
@Elrick wrote:

Greek Mythology successfully created an ideological representation for why common daily occurrences happened.
Greek Mythology has turned into a worldwide phenomenon, finding its way in pop culture and media.
Greek Mythology created an ideal representation of male expectations even to this day (ex: strong, sex driven, physically appealing/perfect, distinct abdominal area, polyamorous = good thing, etc.)

Just some things to think about. Btw you may not want to be so lazy, seeing as you should be taking your education seriously.
